Package org.presentation.graphgenerator.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FullGraphGenerator
    This class can convert graph into SVG image.
    FullGraphGVSGenerator
    This class can convert graph into graphviz source code (no opossum can do that!)
    FullGraphGVSource
    This class represents graphviz source code from FullGraphGVSGenerator.
    FullGraphImage
    This class represents SVG image from FullGraphGenerator.
    GraphTextGenerator
    This class generates graph as text.
    GraphvizSourceCode
    This class represents some graphviz source code.
    GraphvizUtils
    This class can work with Graphviz, tool for generating graphs.
    ReducedGraphGenerator
    This class can convert graph into SVG image with reduced multiedges.
    ReducedGraphGVSGenerator
    This class can convert graph into graphviz source code (no opossum can do that!)
    ReducedGraphGVSource
    This class represents graphviz source code from ReducedGraphGVSGenerator.
    ReducedGraphImage
    This class represents SVG image from ReducedGraphGenerator.
    TraversalGraphTree
    This class represents traversal graph tree by using HTML tags as nested unordered lists.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GraphvizUtils.GraphvizType
    Enum object for identifying graphviz process.
